maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: Hm, I hope we don't get lost around here.
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Hm, j'espère qu'on ne va pas se perdre ici.

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: Seems we have to head \c[3]northwest\c[0] to reach Bergen Trail.
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Il semblerait qu'il faille aller au \c[3]nord-ouest\c[0] pour atteindre le \v[area.bergen-trails.name].

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: I hope it's not too far.
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: J'espère que ce n'est pas trop loin.

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: I will have to logout sooner or later, you see?
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Il va bien falloir que je me déconnecte à un moment ou à un autre.

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: Oh, don't worry. I'll stay until you beat up Mr. Grasshead!
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Oh, ne t'inquiète pas. Je resterais jusqu'à ce que tu battes Monsieur Tête-d'Herbe !

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: And please don't hurry too much because of me!
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Et ne te précipite pas trop à cause de moi !

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: Though there really is no reason for you to prepare for this duel, is there?
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Bien que tu n'aies pas tellement de vraie raison de te préparer pour ce duel, non ?

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: Well, in any case!\. C'est parti!
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Bon, en tout cas !\. C'est parti !

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: We have to make sure you're well trained, non?
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: On doit s'assurer que tu sois bien entraînée, non ?

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: We have been playing for a long while now, Lea.
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Ça va faire un bail qu'on joue, Lea.

maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.orig: Anyway, I suppose there is still time for you to face that duel.
maps/autumn/path5.json/entities/619/sett.text: Mais je pense que tu as encore le temps de faire ce duel.
